snippet: Louis Oosthuizen shot a nine-under 63 in the HSBC Champions in Shenzhen, China, to build a five-shot lead over Ernie Els.
abstract: Louis Oosthuizen takes second-round lead at HSBC Champions golf tournament in Shenzhen, China.
